		<RichText x="738" y="223" width="424" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">距离较远时，黯主进行突棘、横波、纵波至多3段攻击，依次造成<span color="#ffacff">60%,70%,<br/>80%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="479" width="399" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">黯主使用荆尖的尾部造成伤害，造成<span color="#ffacff">25%x3</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="223" width="423" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">黯主跃入空中不见，随后从角色下方突袭，造成<span color="#ffacff">100%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="479" width="424" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">黯主迅速蜷缩并在原地周转一圈，造成<span color="#ffacff">75%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
