		<RichText x="9" y="989" fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="24" fontStyle="normal" fontWeight="normal" color="#ffffff" width="46" height="28" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="1">
			<content>
				<p textAlign="center" fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="24" color="#ffffff">正常</p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="9" y="1049" fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="24" fontStyle="normal" fontWeight="normal" color="#ffffff" width="46" height="28" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="1">
			<content>
				<p textAlign="center" fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="24" color="#ffffff">瘫痪</p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="735" width="422" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">黯主打开后方的传送门并撤入，随后出现在玩家身边，立即甩尾造成<span color="#ffacff">80%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="991" width="426" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">蓄力17s后，黯主吸收所有钓客并消失，随后直接全屏对玩家造成<span color="#ffacff">200%</span><span>伤害</span><span color="#ffbfbf">(闪避帧无效)</span><span>，并在玩家前方重新出现。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="735" width="441" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">黯主吼叫一声，跃入空中，移至场地中央展开「<span textDecoration="underline">深黯护盾</span><span>」，召唤4个「</span><span textDecoration="underline">深黯钓客</span><span>」并开始蓄力。期间「深黯钓客」不附属「深黯护盾」，只会发射激光。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/深黯魇语之主.assets/Image_19.png')" x="719" y="650">
