		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/深黯魇语之主.assets/Image_22.png')" x="64" y="64" blendMode="normal">
		</BitmapImage>
		<RichText x="1410" y="991" width="438" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">黯主蓄力时会展开「深黯护盾」，该护盾为生命盾，并且只接受元素伤害，免疫物理伤害；月曜伤害将造成原来<span color="#ffdfbf">300%</span><span>的伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
