				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="16" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">深黯钓客：特殊的钓客，生命值<span color="#ffdfbf">296145</span><span>(4.86F)(18%黯主生命值)，攻击力</span><span color="#ffdfbf">7832</span><span>(3.0B2)，无护盾，只会发射激光；击败钓客会扣除</span><span color="#ffdfbf">25%</span><span>的深黯护盾。<br/>深黯护盾：</span><span color="#ffdfbf">45%生命值</span><span>盾，击破后黯主损失</span><span color="#ffdfbf">20%生命值</span><span>，并瘫痪16s。</span></p>
